subdirectories.name: assets
subdirectories.sourcedPurposeFromChild: The directory `src\assets` stores the asset files used in a project's source code.

subdirectories.name: components
subdirectories.sourcedPurposeFromChild: This directory, `src\components`, houses the source code for various React components related to a to-do list application, including input, item display, filtering, and statistics functionalities.
